Mason Reese https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mason_Reese 0 Mason Reese (born April 11, 1965) is a former child actor who appeared in numerous television commercials in the 1970s, particularly for Underwood Deviled Ham, Post Raisin Bran, and Dunkin' Donuts.
